# MedRecord Pro — Database Reference Guide

> **Database:** MongoDB Atlas (Cloud)
> **ODM:** Mongoose (Node.js)
> **Total Collections:** 8
> **Architecture:** Normalized, multi-collection with explicit FK references and compound indexes

