## 1. Collections Overview

| # | Collection | PK Field | Role | Has FK Out? | Has FK In? |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `configs` | `email` | Clinic / doctor login & settings | ❌ | ❌ |
| 2 | `patients` | `mobile` | Core patient demographics | ✅ `familyId` | ✅ (visits, appointments, reports, families) |
| 3 | `families` | [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | Groups of linked patients | ✅ `members[].mobile` | ✅ `patients.familyId` |
| 4 | `visits` | [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | Clinical encounter records | ✅ `patientMobile`, `reportIds[]` | ❌ |
| 5 | `appointments` | [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | Scheduled patient appointments | ✅ `patientMobile` | ❌ |
| 6 | `reports` | [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | Uploaded lab/imaging files | ✅ `patientMobile` | ✅ `visits.reportIds[]` |
| 7 | `customdiagnoses` | `name` | User-defined diagnosis terms | ❌ | ❌ |
| 8 | `templates` | `diagnosis` | Preset diagnosis + medicine templates | ❌ | ❌ |

