## 3. Foreign Key Map

| Source Collection | Source Field | Target Collection | Target Field | Cardinality | Required? |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| `patients` | `familyId` | `families` | [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | Many → One | ❌ Optional |
| `families` | `members[].mobile` | `patients` | `mobile` | Many → Many | ✅ Required |
| `visits` | `patientMobile` | `patients` | `mobile` | Many → One | ✅ Required |
| `visits` | `reportIds[]` | `reports` | [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | Many → Many | ❌ Optional |
| `appointments` | `patientMobile` | `patients` | `mobile` | Many → One | ✅ Required |
| `reports` | `patientMobile` | `patients` | `mobile` | Many → One | ✅ Required |

> **Note:** MongoDB does not enforce FK constraints at the engine level.
> Referential integrity is enforced by the server's [validateForeignKeys()](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) function
> (runs on every push-sync, logs warnings for orphaned records).

---

## 4. Subdocument Schemas (Shared)

These are typed schemas embedded **inside** other documents. They are not standalone collections.

### 4.1 Medicine
*Used in: `Visit.medicines[]` and `Template.defaultMedicines[]`*

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) | String | App-generated medicine ID |
| `name` | String | Drug name — **required** |
| `dosage` | String | e.g. `"500mg"` |
| `frequency` | String | e.g. `"1-0-1"` (morning/afternoon/night) |
| `duration` | Number | Number of days |
| `instructions` | String | e.g. `"Take with food"` |

> `_id` is suppressed — medicines are identified by [id](file:///c:/Users/bhavi/Desktop/bhavik%20docs/Digitifi/works/emr%20software/server.js#281-321) within the app.

---

### 4.2 Vitals
*Used in: `Visit.vitals`*

| Field | Type | Unit | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| `weight` | Number | kg | Body weight |
| `height` | Number | cm | Height |
| `bmi` | Number | — | Body Mass Index |
| `temp` | Number | °F | Body temperature |
| `pulse` | Number | bpm | Heart rate |
| `bp_sys` | Number | mmHg | Systolic blood pressure |
| `bp_dia` | Number | mmHg | Diastolic blood pressure |
| `spo2` | Number | % | Oxygen saturation |
| `respRate` | Number | breaths/min | Respiratory rate |

---

### 4.3 FamilyMember
*Used in: `Family.members[]`*

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `mobile` | String | **FK → patients.mobile** |
| `relationship` | String | e.g. `"Spouse"`, `"Child"`, `"Self"` |

